sources.description:
Where fur and foul play collide!  
Detective Philo Vance investigates the murder of a wealthy collector during a dog show. With a multitude of suspects, Vance must unravel the mystery and identify the killer before they strike again.

Original title: The Kennel Murder Case (1933)

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/JX2oaio8nlM

Director: Michael Curtiz
Writers: S.S. Van Dine 
Stars: William Powell, Mary Astor, Eugene Pallette 
Genres: Colorized classics, Crime, Film Noir, Mystery

Many subtitles available for this movie
